openai-codex.git/

  fork of openai/codex
  Make changes here, then push to github.

Running `codex` in this directory will allow Codex to work on the openai-codex.git repository.

openai-codex/

  source tree with PKGBUILD, downloaded with:

    pkgctl repo clone --protocol=https openai-codex

  PKGBUILD was changed; see PKGBUILD.diff

To (re)compile, run `makepkg -si` in openai-codex/.

Alternatively, have

daniel:~/projects/github/codex/openai-codex/src>ls -l
total 4
lrwxrwxrwx 1 carlo carlo 22 Dec 19 18:12 openai-codex -> ../../openai-codex.git

and run `makepkg --noextract --noprepare --nocheck --install`.
